**Addendum 2:** The following transcript details an incident featuring Sancho Martel Aznar, a janitor at Site-211, who was assigned the maintenance of SCP-6508. Agent Blasco Samper Ruiz was also assigned to this task to secure the safety of the janitor.

[[size 1%]]##transparent|.##[[/size]]

[[include :scp-wiki:component:blacklight-box-source |inc-section-start= --]
|color-family= optional-colors
|unique-name= lowercase-nospaces
|display-name= TRANSCRIPT OF VIDEO RECORDING
]]

**DATE/TIME:** 15/01/2021 23:49

**PERSONNEL PRESENT:**

* Agent Blasco Samper Ruiz
* Sancho Martel Aznar

----

[[=]]
**<BEGIN LOG>**
[[/=]]

//<Mr. Martel is seen entering the building, followed by Agent Samper who locks the door behind him. Mr. Martel dresses in the protective suit he was given and a tool belt with cleaning products.>//

**Agent Samper:** You're good. Go ahead.

//<Mr. Martel cleans one of SCP-6508's aquariums. Before he can start cleaning the next one, he is interrupted by Agent Samper.>//

**Agent Samper:** Isn't it hot in here?

//<Mr. Martel turns back and looks at him with a frowned expression, followed by unrecognizable mumbling.>//

**Agent Samper:** Can you take off the thing for a second? I can't hear you with the noise of all of the fans.

//<Mr. Martel removes the headpiece from his suit and sighs before speaking again.>//

**Sancho Martel:** Yeah. The wavemakers, the dosing pumps, and all that stuff produce a lot of heat. 

**Agent Samper:** Do you know a lot about aquariums?

//<Mr. Martel shakes his head.>//

**Sancho Martel:** They gave me a mini-seminar before assigning me to this task.

**Agent Samper:** I see.

//<Both of them remain silent. Moments later, Mr. Martel resumes his task and begins cleaning the second aquarium.>//

**Agent Samper:** The Foundation loves keeping their secrets, don't they? They tell us the bare minimum we need to know and nothing else. I used to be close to Fátima before getting lured into this shithole. All we talk about these days is work.

//<Mr. Martel continues with this task, unbothered by Agent Samper's rant.>//

**Agent Samper:** Fuck. I'm sorry, I didn't mean to just start rambling out of nowhere.

**Sancho Martel:** It's okay. I don't mind.

//<A few seconds of silence.>//

**Sancho Martel:** Wait. Fátima? The Site Director? 

**Agent Samper:** The one and only. She was the one who got me to join the Foundation. When I got in, she had already been working here for a decade. She's good at everything she does, I'm not surprised she became a Site Director. Hell, I won't be surprised if she ever becomes part of the Overseer Council or whatever is at the top of the pyramid. What about you, Sancho?

**Sancho Martel:** Well, I'm an only child so I don't know what having a sibling is like. Though, sometimes I wish I had one who helped me to get through tough times.

**Agent Samper:** Fátima used to be like that when we were younger. Even though she always got perfect grades and the approval of our parents, she'd always make sure I'm okay.

**Sancho Martel:** That must've been nice-

//<An octopus splashes Mr. Martel while he is distracted by the conversation.>//

**Sancho Martel:** Shit.

//<Agent Samper runs to Sancho.>//

**Agent Samper:** Are you okay, Sancho?

**Sancho Martel:** Just a bit dizzy. Shit. The suit. I didn't put the headpiece back on.

**Agent Samper:** Calm down. It's gonna be okay, you're gonna make it.

**Sancho Martel:** But something is gonna happen to me, isn't it? Please tell me it won't hurt.

**Agent Samper:** I-I- No, no. It won't.

//<Agent Samper brings clean towels for Mr. Martel to dry himself. Sancho looks nauseous and barely can keep his equilibrium.>//

**Sancho Martel:** What's gonna happen to me? Am I going to be contained?

//<Agent Samper holds Mr. Martel by the shoulder.>//

**Agent Samper:** Let's go get you back to Site-211. Everything is going to be okay. I promise.

[[=]]
**<END LOG>**
[[/=]]

----

[[include :scp-wiki:component:blacklight-box-source |inc-section-end= --]]]

[[size 1%]]##transparent|.##[[/size]]

After the events of the previous transcript, Mr. Martel became an SCP-6508-1 instance. His head assumed the form of an //octopus vulgaris//, almost identical to the one inside SCP-6508. The skin tone of the superior part of Mr. Martel's arms is now a hue matching the one of his head and presents several suction cups.

After some discussion, it was decided that Mr. Martel would keep his position as a janitor on Site-211 and now he would be permanently assigned to SCP-6508's maintenance.

